description: Customers rave about the delicious pizza's served up by Mattie's Wood Fired Pizza. Their menu features a variety of classic pizzas,as well as other italian food favorites  that will be sure to please both meat lovers and vegetarians. If you'd like to hire them for catering your event small or large they can even customize a menu, or even create original menu items to your liking.
name: Mattie's Wood Fired Pizza & Catering
